lead_paragraph: Across the country, protesters gathered in large numbers to voice their opinions on an executive order signed by President Trump that restricted entry into the U.S. for some Muslims.

byline.original: By NIRAJ CHOKSHI and NICHOLAS FANDOS
byline.contributor: Reporting was contributed by Thomas Fuller, Eric Lipton, Fernanda Santos and Jonathan Wolfe.

headline.main: Demonstrators in Streets, and at Airports, Protest Immigration Order
headline.print_headline: Demonstrators in Streets and at Airports Protest Trump Order on Immigration
